						<summary>

						<p>Stone near <hi rend="italic">gādi</hi> bhāvi, on the road side, north of the village.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 142[9], Prabhava, Kārttika śu. 1[5], [Sunday],</hi> Irregular.</p>						

						<p>Records the gift of some lands in Mārkapuram by Mahāmanḍalēśvara Salakarāju Timmayadēva Mahārāja, and refers to a tank in the village Gūḍūru.</p>						

